DevFlow is an independent, ground-up reimplementation. Its phase-loop discipline
— fresh-context subagents, wave-parallel execution, plan checking, goal-backward
verification, and durable .planning/ state — is derived in concept from GSD:

  GSD Core (open-gsd/gsd-core) — MIT License
  Copyright (c) 2026 Open GSD
  https://github.com/open-gsd/gsd-core

No source files from GSD Core are included in DevFlow; the behavioral contracts
were reimplemented in a compressed, Claude-Code-only form. This notice is
provided as attribution under the spirit of the MIT License.
